    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造・自定义・驾驶</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《绝境刹车手》是一款强调技巧胜过速度的街机精准驾驶游戏。驰骋在充满障碍的刺激赛道上，每一次闪避、漂移和转向都极度考验你的操控能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战一系列高强度驾驶任务，全面提升你的反应力和创造力！完成各种高难度目标，从极速冲刺到躲避陷阱的精准操控，无论是闪避危险还是追求极致，每个关卡都将考验你的驾驶技术！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256300/extras/7379fa7c759712372a1416f9917deac3.poster.avif?t=1759424628\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256300/extras/7379fa7c759712372a1416f9917deac3.webm?t=1759424628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256300/extras/7379fa7c759712372a1416f9917deac3.mp4?t=1759424628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>街机精准驾驶</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受流畅紧凑的操控，技巧与创意并存！灵活闪避陷阱、大胆挑战高难度动作，并以最华丽的方式抵达神秘雕像！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>车辆自定义</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级你的车辆，征服更严峻的挑战！调整速度与操控性，自定义车身涂装，打造独一无二的风格，迎接每一场比赛！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>对战小游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邀请朋友加入本地多人混战！在“夺旗挑战”、“炸弹接力”和“生存挑战”等模式中一较高下，看看谁才是真正的驾驶王者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态关卡</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >征服充满变数的赛道，激光、移动平台、爆炸桶等创意机关让每场比赛都充满挑战！随机应变、极限操作，突破你的驾驶极限！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256300/extras/c31b86cd1545444bca74fae51f5b2487.poster.avif?t=1759424628\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256300/extras/c31b86cd1545444bca74fae51f5b2487.webm?t=1759424628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256300/extras/c31b86cd1545444bca74fae51f5b2487.mp4?t=1759424628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
